name: The Witch
description: Technology made magic obsolete. The vast superiority of instant gratification let ancient art go into a sort of soft-extinction. The books, the mana, all of that never disappeared. Just not a soul to use it. Except her. She wanted to revive the ancient art. Clout was the way. Gaining as much virality as possible by winning the Sky Derby. She didn't like to stand out, but she knew it was the only effective way to revive what she cherish the most. And even that might be a stretch, but sometime you just have to try...
